<li class='cover' id='bookCover_17349'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17349.The_Demon_Haunted_World"><img alt="The Demon-Haunted World: Science as a Candle in the Dark" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1553691804l/17349._SX98_.jpg" />
</a>

  
