<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15766601-the-world-until-yesterday"><img alt="The World Until Yesterday: What Can We Learn from Traditional Societies?" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1461046572l/15766601._SX98_.jpg" />
